  "narrative": {
    "northStar": "Editorial, cinematic, type-led. The home page reads like a printed editorial spread set in motion — display type at 80–96px, white ground, scroll-driven mosaic hero, one saturated blue. The portfolio reads as one system across 30 products.",
    "rules": [
      "Type leads. Color and ornament come second.",
      "Whitespace is the grid.",
      "Motion is structural, not decorative.",
      "Image is editorial — full-bleed cards, no stock-photo afterthoughts.",
